mann\">Werner Inmann</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 30, 1998</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Iterative_Deepening&amp;action=edit&amp;section=12\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=156310\">Iterative deepening deep increment</a> by <a href=\"/Alvaro_Cardoso\" title=\"Alvaro Cardoso\">Alvaro Jose Povoa Cardoso</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 27, 2001 </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=14963\">iterative deepening and branching factor</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=J._Wesley_Cleveland&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"J. Wesley Cleveland (page does not exist)\">J. Wesley Cleveland</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 09, 2007&#160;» <a href=\"/Branching_Factor#EffectiveBranchingFactor\" title=\"Branching Factor\">Effective Branching Factor</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=4&amp;t=6666\">Even more search questions</a> by <a href=\"/Sven_Sch%C3%BCle\" title=\"Sven Schüle\">Sven Schüle</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, July 17, 2007</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Iterative_Deepening&amp;action=edit&amp;section=13\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-chess.org/viewtopic.php?f=5&amp;t=1403\">